 1993-03131993-02-220,  ,  COM,  , 
PrecisAppointment of Peter Senchuk, of Edmonton, Alberta, as a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; designation of the said Peter Senchuk for the Alberta/Northwest Territories region, as estblished under subsection 10(1.1) of that Act; and determine that he shall reside within 100 kilometres of the Alberta/Northwest Territories regional office.
